data.description: SIX LOTS situated just minutes from the lake! This property spans across six fenced lots in the subdivision and features a large workshop with a half bath. Two carports provide lots of parking. Inside, this home features three bedrooms, two bathrooms, two fireplaces, a dine-in kitchen, and two living areas. One of the living areas is a flex space that could be used as a living room, bedroom, game room. Schedule your showing today!
